{"tid":1388524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(幫推) 黑驚係仆街，但大家唔好忘記五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:26:40.000Z","uid":160887,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"783e8a66d5021bf725d8d9e48347a533943fd98c","tid":1388524,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:10:24.000Z","msg":"警察的確係做咗好多仆街野，<br />\n但係我哋唔好忘記當初點解要企出嚟，<br />\n就係因為反送中同埋爭取真民主<br />\n<br />\n雖然今晚光頭佬俾人打， <br />\n大家都睇到好開心<br />\n但大家唔好忘記我地仲有成180個義士俾人困住咗<br />\n可能要背上暴動罪，襲警等等罪名<br />\n<br />\n到呢一步其實真正勇敢行出黎嘅人做前線嘅真係為數唔係太多，<br />\n希望大家嘅視線唔好咁易俾人轉移，對準政權"},{"pid":"76b7892465b98f2e9689d47795eb11a4da7a91b0","tid":1388524,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6226cc506345693b1518301d3af609f492ff5d2","tid":1388524,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:10:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8180ef6f5dfe59bc7a06fe78a3a81ecaeca74a66","tid":1388524,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:10:50.000Z","msg":"承認吧，夢中已沒法治，戰場只講力量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c61936d080a0e699a5dcebfc3db70b8a9476b54f","tid":1388524,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:11:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8283ca4230fdf8902cec5db3b106a7d0896b02b9","tid":1388524,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7be4d0c64e79f604db98620003a6b8d90429a1bc","tid":1388524,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"幫推啦屌"},{"pid":"8f65d9ac87704d849c89575a026dd059fff05e87","tid":1388524,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad27713203f500d0002d1bb4152434dcad0f1c9","tid":13